Author: swords_zz
Content:
This might be a sensitive topic. But I want to get this outta my head.

After seeing so many news & posts about what's going on currently, I feel like I lost faith on this country, little by little. But then again, I still live here.

Is it wrong to feel that way? 
What should I do, or how can I deal with it?

Author: shiawase6946
Content: Focus on yourself; sharpen your skills, learn new skills, study more start a business, etc. At the end of the day your fate is yours to made.
